sections.heading: to 69-19-19 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-19-1 to 69-19-19 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 102 to 106, 108, 109, and 113 to 120 , relating to explosives in mines, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
